Author: ilovegibbyhaynes
Text: oh, i know. that’s what i was saying, like, it isn’t her job to compliment me haha. just silly thoughts that run through my head instead of just accepting a compliment.

Author: bongshelter
Text: I don't think compliments are part of the job at Kroger. That was just her honest opinion. It would be less believable from someone trying to sell you clothes or beauty related products.  I get it though... I can't take compliments seriously if the person giving it is thinner or prettier. Being called "skinny" just seems sarcastic somehow.
